it was used as the name of a cheerful and scantily clad beauty whose adventures were chronicled in a strip cartoon in the Daily Mirror. It is also borne by the American film stars  Jane Russell  (  1921–2011 ) and  Jane Fonda  (  b. 1937 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Jeanne was born in 1420. She had at least 3 sons and 1 daughter with Didier de Thiesselin."},"et":{"1420–":"1420–Surnud","1420–1483":"1420–1483","1460–Female":"1460–Surnud","1470–1517":"1470–1517","–1516":"–1516","–Male":"Surnud","1420–Female":"1420–Surnud","1420":"1420","1483":"1483","1460":"1460","1470":"1470","1517":"1517","1516":"1516","Fressingfield, Suffolk, England":"Fressingfield, Suffolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1420–":"1420–Kuollut","1420–1483":"1420–1483","1460–Female":"1460–Kuollut","1470–1517":"1470–1517","–1516":"–1516","–Male":"Kuollut","1420–Female":"1420–Kuollut","1420":"1420","1483":"1483","1460":"1460","1470":"1470","1517":"1517","1516":"1516","Fressingfield, Suffolk, England":"Fressingfield, Suffolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1420–":"1420–Décédée","1420–1483":"1420–1483","1460–Female":"1460–Décédée","1470–1517":"1470–1517","–1516":"–1516","–Male":"Décédé","1420–Female":"1420–Décédée","1420":"1420","1483":"1483","1460":"1460","1470":"1470","1517":"1517","1516":"1516","Fressingfield, Suffolk, England":"Fressingfield, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Jeanne est née en 1420. Elle a eu au moins 3 fils et 1 fille avec Didier de Thiesselin."},"de":{"1420–":"1420–Verstorben","1420–1483":"1420–1483","1460–Female":"1460–Verstorben","1470–1517":"1470–1517","–1516":"–1516","–Male":"Verstorben","1420–Female":"1420–Verstorben","1420":"1420","1483":"1483","1460":"1460","1470":"1470","1517":"1517","1516":"1516","Fressingfield, Suffolk, England":"Fressingfield, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Jeanne wurde 1420 geboren. Sie hatte mit Didier de Thiesselin mindestens 3 Söhne und 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1420–":"1420–Desede","1420–1483":"1420–1483","1460